# PPIA IU Website

A dynamic website for the Indonesian Student Association at Indiana University (PPIA IU).

## ğŸ“‹ Description

This is a dynamic web platform built to manage information and activities for PPIA IU. The website provides content management features, user authentication, and file storage using MongoDB GridFS.

## ğŸš€ Tech Stack

### Backend
- **Node.js** - JavaScript runtime environment
- **Express.js** (v4.19.2) - Web framework for Node.js
- **MongoDB** (v5.9.1) - NoSQL database
- **Mongoose** (v8.5.2) - ODM (Object Data Modeling) for MongoDB

### Template Engine & Frontend
- **EJS** (v3.1.10) - Embedded JavaScript templating
- **EJS Mate** (v4.0.0) - Layout and partial support for EJS
- **CSS** - Styling (46.1% of codebase)
- **JavaScript** (22.8% of codebase)
- **GSAP** (v3.12.5) - JavaScript animation library

### Authentication & Security
- **Passport.js** (v0.7.0) - Authentication middleware
- **Passport Local Mongoose** (v8.0.0) - Local authentication strategy for Mongoose
- **Express Session** (v1.18.0) - Session management
- **Crypto** (v1.0.1) - Encryption and hashing

### File Upload & Storage
- **Multer** (v1.4.4) - Middleware for handling multipart/form-data
- **Multer GridFS Storage** (v5.0.2) - Storage engine for storing files in MongoDB GridFS
- **GridFS Stream** (v1.1.1) - Streaming files from GridFS

### Utilities & Middleware
- **Body Parser** (v1.20.3) - Parse request bodies
- **Cookie Parser** (v1.4.7) - Parse cookies
- **Method Override** (v3.0.0) - Support for HTTP verbs (PUT, DELETE)
- **Connect Flash** (v0.1.1) - Flash messages
- **Joi** (v17.13.3) - Data validation and schema
- **Dotenv** (v16.4.5) - Environment variables management

