## ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture

This project follows the **MVC (Model-View-Controller)** pattern:

- **Models** (`/models`) - Database schemas and data logic using Mongoose
- **Views** (`/views`) - EJS templates for rendering HTML
- **Controllers** (`/controllers`) - Business logic and request handling
- **Routes** (`/routes`) - API endpoints and route definitions
- **Middlewares** (`/middlewares`) - Custom middleware functions
- **Schemas** (`/schemas`) - Joi validation schemas

